snippet.title: Spaceship for Newbies - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The planet Xanar is a big deposit of junk and debris. In an attempt to change this situation and reduce the amount of trash on the planet, a team of engineers and scientists developed a spaceship made entirely of scrap, which can be controlled by pressing one button! 

You’re the test pilot of this spaceship. Can you fly it through the obstacles in outer space?

WISHLIST NOW

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1568130/Spaceship_for_Newbies/
Itch.io: https://molotov-estudios.itch.io/spaceship-for-newbies
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.MolotovEstdios.SpaceshipforNewbies

Twitter: https://twitter.com/molotovestudio/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/molotovestudios/
Discord: https://discord.gg/sJuR9tct

Music and sound: Punkhazard Studios (https://www.instagram.com/punkhazardstudios/)
